  "texts": [
    "The SFT model trained with tool use is denoted as RAVEN.",
    "When tool use fails due to ill-formed arguments we have a fallback mechanism to produce the answer by the SFT model, denoted as BACKOFF.",
    "For training details and hardware, see Appendix B.",
    "We evaluate the models using exact match.",
    "The task router has determined the correct type 100% of the time, except for TAT-QA where the accuracy was 90.62%."
